snippet.textDisplay: Not going to lie, I was religious about my coffee go about 5 years. I ground my own beans using a burr grinder, and used a French press with a timer. The coffee was good, and I enjoyed it. However, one day I had some bog standard maxwell house. It was amazing, and now I own a bunn, only use maxwell house, and my coffee is fantastic. It really isnt worth all of the hassle of multi step coffee snobbery.
